%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Welcome%20to%20the%20summer%20of%20the%20staycation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227360%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20relaxes%20in%20a%20beach%20chair%20in%20his%20living%20room.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c558e2299090a8c09b68f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224912%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Edemaerre%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Crook%20family%20is%20trying%20to%20ignore%20one%20thing%20hanging%20over%20their%20approaching%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoing-to-hawaii-first-time-tips-mistakes-oahu%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHawaiian%20vacation%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20might%20not%20happen.%20Granted%2C%20it%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20first%20time%20they've%20changed%20plans%20this%20year.%20They%20initially%20wanted%20to%20go%20to%20Canc%C3%BAn%2C%20but%20they%20scrapped%20that%20idea%20due%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpuerto-vallarta-mexico-tourism-shelter-in-place-cartel-violence-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunrest%20in%20Mexico%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February.%20They%20instead%20pivoted%20to%20Maui%2C%20but%20the%20getaway%20is%20on%20the%20books%20in%20pencil%2C%20not%20pen.%20They%20intentionally%20booked%20accommodations%20with%20lax%20cancellation%20policies%2C%20and%20if%20they%20wind%20up%20dropping%20their%20flights%2C%20at%20least%20they'll%20get%20to%20keep%20the%20airline%20credit.%20%26quot%3BEverything's%20kind%20of%20hedged%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Colin%20Crook%2C%2051%2C%20the%20California%20family's%20patriarch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrook's%20wife%20is%20a%20teacher%2C%20meaning%20there's%20little%20wiggle%20room%20for%20vacations%20outside%20the%20summer%20months.%20He%20does%20freelance%20PR%2C%20which%20is%20more%20flexible%20in%20terms%20of%20scheduling%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforget-ai-heres-the-real-reason-the-job-market-sucks-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eless%20stable%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20terms%20of%20job%20security.%20%26quot%3BThe%20economic%20uncertainty%20of%20being%20a%20laptop%20warrior%20%E2%80%94%20as%20an%20email%20professional%20or%20a%20white-collar%20professional%20right%20now%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20just%20very%20up%20in%20the%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BWith%20everything%20going%20on%20in%20the%20economy%20and%20the%20world%2C%20we%20just%20feel%20like%20it's%20like%20month%20to%20month%2C%20what%20can%20we%20do%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Americans%20are%20weighing%20similar%20issues.%20It's%20a%20complicated%20moment%20for%20travel%20planning.%20The%20United%20States'%20war%20in%20Iran%20has%20caused%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrikes-on-iran-flights-canceled-diverted-busiest-airspace-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emajor%20travel%20disruptions%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20and%20it's%20led%20to%20a%20spike%20in%20oil%20prices%2C%20making%20fuel%20and%20gas%20%E2%80%94%20and%20therefore%20flights%20and%20drives%20%E2%80%94%20more%20expensive.%20It's%20upped%20anxiety%20for%20consumers%20and%20workers%20who%20are%20already%20on%20edge%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-smart-people-saying-about-inflation-energy-prices-iran-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabout%20inflation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20job%20market%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-economy-recession-outlook-gdp-iran-mark-zandi-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20potential%20recession%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Americans%20aren't%20exactly%20feeling%20the%20love%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftravel-trump-tariffs-america-international-canada-europe-flights-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrom%20foreign%20hosts%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20of%20late%2C%20either%2C%20given%20the%20White%20House's%20antagonistic%20foreign%20policy%20stances%20and%20general%20tourism%20fatigue%20in%20some%20desirable%20destinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20spring%20and%20summer%20travel%20seasons%20upon%20us%2C%20Americans%20are%20considering%20a%20pared-down%20option%3A%20staying%20local.%20Taking%20a%20getaway%20without%20actually%20getting%20away%20can%20save%20money%2C%20avoid%20travel%20chaos%2C%20and%20represent%20a%20low-lift%2C%20low-stress%20option%20for%20some%20R%26amp%3BR.%20When%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20world%20feels%20uncertain%2C%20there's%20a%20comforting%20level%20of%20security%20in%20sticking%20close%20to%20home.%20And%20hey%2C%2011%20US%20cities%20have%20World%20Cup%20matches%2C%20so%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20afford%20tickets%20instead%20of%20an%20increasingly%20expensive%20flight%20to%20France.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20hope%20springs%20eternal%20for%20a%20Hawaiian%20holiday%2C%20Crook%20has%20set%20a%20mental%20deadline%20of%20mid-April%20to%20decide%20whether%20to%20pull%20the%20plug.%20If%20he%20does%2C%20there%20are%20options%20closer%20to%20home.%20%26quot%3BWe%20might%20just%20be%20camping%20a%20lot%20this%20summer%2C%20which%20is%20fine%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%202025%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Froadtrips-falling-gas-prices-economic-fears-how-to-save-vacation-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyear%20of%20the%20road%20trip%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%202026%20may%20be%20the%20year%20of%20the%20staycation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20Americans%20appear%20to%20be%20cooling%20on%20international%20jaunts%2C%20including%20frequent%20foreign%20travelers.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyougov.com%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F53736-americans-pull-back-on-global-travel-heading-into-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPolling%20last%20fall%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20YouGov%20found%20that%2043%25%20of%20respondents%20who%20travel%20abroad%20regularly%20did%20so%20less%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20citing%20personal%20issues%2C%20economic%20uncertainty%2C%20and%20rising%20travel%20costs.%20A%20recent%20analysis%20by%20Cirium%2C%20an%20aviation%20analytics%20company%2C%20found%20that%20third-party%20air%20travel%20bookings%20from%20US%20hubs%20to%20major%20European%20cities%20this%20summer%20have%20fallen%20by%2011%25%20compared%20to%20last%20year.%20(The%20number%20of%20Europeans%20coming%20to%20the%20US%20is%20down%20even%20more%20sharply.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsistent%20with%20prior%20episodes%2C%20I%20anticipate%20a%20move%20toward%20closer%2C%20less%20expensive%20vacation%20destinations%20will%20occur%20naturally%2C%20as%20a%20function%20of%20economic%20concerns%20driving%20greater%20affordability%2C%20and%20geopolitics%20driving%20some%20away%20from%20areas%20with%20greater%20perceived%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Bob%20Mann%2C%20an%20aviation%20analyst.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20aren't%20just%20thinking%20twice%20about%20going%20abroad%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20taking%20a%20hard%20look%20at%20where%20they're%20going%20Stateside.%20For%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipx1031.com%2Famericans-travel-report-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espring%20break%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20people%20are%20planning%20to%20stick%20close%20to%20home%20or%20skip%20a%20trip%20entirely%2C%20due%20to%20economic%20concerns%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-lines-atlanta-houston-united-delta-waive-change-fees-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETSA%20headaches%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20high%20gas%20and%20fuel%20prices%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipsos.com%2Fen-us%2Fgas-prices-arent-hurting-americans-summer-plans-yet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edon't%20appear%20to%20be%3C%2Fa%3E%20significantly%20affecting%20domestic%20summer%20travel%20plans%20yet%2C%20that%20could%20change%20as%20the%20warmer%20months%20approach%2C%20especially%20if%20the%20price%20at%20the%20pump%20stays%20elevated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20feel%20stuck%20between%20a%20rock%20and%20a%20hard%20place%3A%20Do%20they%20book%20a%20flight%20now%20out%20of%20fear%20the%20cost%20equation%20will%20get%20worse%2C%20or%20do%20they%20hold%20off%20and%20hope%20for%20some%20relief%3F%20And%20if%20they%20do%20eschew%20the%20plane%20ticket%2C%20how%20good%20will%20they%20feel%20about%20that%20July%20road%20trip%20if%20gas%20is%20%244%2C%20%245%2C%20or%20%246%20a%20gallon%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatrick%20De%20Haan%2C%20the%20head%20of%20petroleum%20analysis%20at%20GasBuddy%2C%20a%20fuel%20price-tracking%20app%2C%20tells%20me%20the%20outlook%20is%20extremely%20murky%2C%20given%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20in%20Iran%20and%20its%20effective%20blockage%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsecuring-strait-of-hormuz-isnt-easy-even-with-navy-analysts-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStrait%20of%20Hormuz%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20world's%20most%20important%20oil%20route.%20Gas%20prices%20are%20already%20up%20by%20%241%20per%20gallon%20over%20the%20past%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20the%20situation%20continues%20and%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20sees%20no%20meaningful%20improvement%20in%20terms%20of%20ships%20navigating%20through%2C%20gas%20prices%20will%20continue%20to%20go%20up.%20And%20there's%20really%20not%20necessarily%20a%20ceiling%20on%20how%20high%20prices%20will%20go%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECruises%20may%20not%20be%20immune%20to%20the%20economic%20context%2C%20either.%20Many%20cruise%20lines%20added%20fuel%20surcharges%20in%202008%20to%20offset%20rising%20oil%20prices%2C%20and%20there%20are%20concerns%20they%20could%20do%20so%20again.%20One%20line%2C%20in%20Asia%2C%20already%20has%2C%20and%20it's%20in%20the%20fine%20print%20for%20many%20cruise%20lines%20that%20they%20can%2C%20whether%20you've%20booked%20already%20or%20not.%20Royal%20Ahmadi%2C%20the%20senior%20vice%20president%20and%20general%20manager%20of%20The%20Vacation%20Group%2C%20a%20leisure%20travel%20agency%20that%20focuses%20on%20cruises%2C%20tells%20me%20he%20thinks%20cruise%20lines%20are%20better%20prepared%20to%20absorb%20the%20blow.%20%26quot%3BThey%20already%20pre-planned%20a%20lot%20of%20that%20stuff%2C%20so%20this%20way%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20raise%20the%20prices%20to%20accommodate%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20Above%20all%2C%20his%20clients%20are%20concerned%20about%20TSA%20lines%2C%20but%20he%20says%20they're%20generally%20forging%20ahead%20with%20bookings%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20only%20the%20direct%20cost%20of%20travel%20that's%20making%20people%20sweat.%20Americans%20may%20see%20their%20budgets%20tighten%20thanks%20to%20exceptionally%20high%20diesel%20prices.%20Since%20diesel%20is%20used%20by%20trucks%20to%20transport%20all%20the%20basics%20we%20need%2C%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20higher%20prices%20across%20the%20board%20%E2%80%94%20leaving%20families%20with%20less%20money%20to%20book%20a%20faraway%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%202008%20buzzword%20'staycation'%20is%20coming%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20De%20Haan%20says%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tough%20comparison%20given%20that%20it%20was%20a%20moment%20when%20the%20economy%20was%20in%20freefall%20and%20gas%20prices%20exploded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EEconomics%20aside%2C%20there%20are%20other%20reasons%20people%20might%20want%20to%20keep%20their%20adventures%20a%20little%20less%20adventurous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConcerns%20about%20overtourism%20sparked%20a%20backlash%20against%20foreign%20visitors%20in%20popular%20destinations%20such%20as%20Italy%2C%20Spain%2C%20and%20Japan.%20Americans%3A%20If%20you're%20frustrated%20to%20be%20surrounded%20by%20a%20bunch%20of%20%3Cem%3Eother%20%3C%2Fem%3EAmericans%20in%20Barcelona%2C%20imagine%20how%20the%20Barcelonans%20feel.%20The%20city%20is%20doubling%20its%20tourist%20tax%20to%20drive%20home%20the%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDonald%20Trump's%20foreign%20policy%20isn't%20helping%20either.%20The%20president%20has%20alienated%20multiple%20allies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanada-moment-mark-carney-reshaping-economy-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincluding%20Canada%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20many%20European%20Union%20countries%2C%20over%20issues%20such%20as%20trade%20and%20defense.%20US%20strikes%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20have%20caused%20global%20disruption.%20As%20much%20as%20foreigners%20are%20aware%20that%20individual%20American%20tourists%20are%20not%20responsible%20for%20the%20White%20House's%20decisions%2C%20they%20may%20not%20be%20thrilled%20to%20welcome%20a%20brigade%20of%20star-spangled%20visitors%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESafety%20concerns%20are%20playing%20a%20factor%20for%20some%20Americans%20as%20well.%20In%20February%2C%20drug%20cartel%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20Mexico%2C%20leaving%20many%20travelers%20stranded.%20Of%20course%2C%20spending%20a%20week%20completely%20protected%20and%20locked%20in%20a%20high-end%20resort%20is%20not%20the%20worst-case%20scenario%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20ideal%2C%20either.%20In%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20US%20and%20Israel's%20attacks%20on%20Iran%20and%20Iran's%20retaliation%2C%20many%20people%20found%20themselves%20in%20places%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20that%20became%20dangerous%20overnight.%20The%20US%20State%20Department%20recently%20issued%20a%20%26quot%3Bworldwide%20caution%26quot%3B%20alert%2C%20warning%20Americans%20everywhere%20to%20be%20extra%20careful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDan%20Ahern%2C%2027%2C%20tells%20me%20he's%20%26quot%3Bmonitoring%20the%20situation%26quot%3B%20ahead%20of%20his%20June%20trip%20to%20Armenia%2C%20which%20shares%20a%20short%20border%20with%20Iran.%20The%20New%20York-based%20communications%20professional's%20travel%20plans%20are%20full-speed%20ahead%20for%20now%2C%20though%20he's%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20news%20and%20the%20State%20Department's%20travel%20advisory%20list%20on%20his%20radar.%20He's%20also%20worried%20about%20anti-American%20sentiment.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20uncertainty%20in%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20travel%20experience%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20every%20vacation%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20staycation%2C%20but%20if%20there's%20ever%20a%20year%20to%20do%20it%2C%202026%20could%20be%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20domestic%20destinations%20could%20use%20an%20economic%20boost%2C%20especially%20due%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforeign-travelers-avoiding-us-continued-blow-to-tourism-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrop%20in%20international%20tourism%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20US.%20That%20means%20shorter%20lines%20and%20better%20deals%20in%20places%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-parks-international-visitors-down-foreign-travelers-us-slowdown-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDisney%20World%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20the%20Grand%20Canyon%20that%20are%20typically%20swamped%20with%20foreign%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorld%20Cup%20matches%20will%20be%20within%20striking%20distance%2C%20literally%20and%20figuratively%2C%20for%20many%20Americans%2C%20especially%20as%20lower-priced%20tickets%20become%20available.%20For%20someone%20in%20New%20York%20or%20New%20Jersey%2C%20MetLife%20Stadium%20is%20only%20a%20(slightly%20miserable)%20train%20or%20bus%20ride%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20no%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspent-four-hours-at-tsa-jfk-the-situation-felt-dangerous-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETSA%20lines%20required%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20finally%20cleaning%20out%20your%20closet%2C%20catching%20up%20on%20your%20reading%2C%20or%20visiting%20that%20cute%20local%20gallery%20you've%20been%20meaning%20to%20check%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20freedom%20in%20exploring%20an%20island%20in%20Greece.%20There's%20also%20freedom%20in%20knowing%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20respond%20to%20a%207%20am%20email%20from%20your%20boss%20for%20a%20week%2C%20even%20if%20you're%20not%20responding%20from%20the%20comfort%20of%20your%20own%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%20business%20and%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsummer-travel-america-stay-home-staycation-high-oil-prices-tsa-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774772521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c558ff299090a8c09b68fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsummer-travel-america-stay-home-staycation-high-oil-prices-tsa-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22High%20oil%20prices%20and%20travel%20uncertainty%20are%20stoking%20anxiety%20and%20jeopardizing%20summer%20vacation%20plans.%20More%20Americans%20are%20opting%20to%20stay%20at%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22estewart%40insider.com%20(Emily%20Stewart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsummer-travel-america-stay-home-staycation-high-oil-prices-tsa-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20chokehold%3A%20What%20is%20happening%20to%20petrol%20prices%20in%20India%20and%20neighbouring%20nations%20amid%20oil%20supply%20crunch%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774771924000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129877579%2Cimgsize-181388.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Finternational-business%2Fstrait-of-