%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EModern%20cars%20are%20equipped%20with%20sensors%20to%20support%20driver%20assistance%20systems%20and%20safety%20features.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKinetic%20is%20a%20startup%20that%20provides%20sensor%20calibration%20after%20a%20car%20is%20involved%20in%20a%20collision.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKinetic%20CEO%20Nikhil%20Naikal%20said%20his%20company%20aims%20to%20service%20autonomous%20vehicle%20fleets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobotaxis-change-role-of-human-drivers-uber-chief-says-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHuman%20drivers%3C%2Fa%3E%20aren't%20the%20only%20ones%20who%20need%20to%20have%20eyes%20on%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20cars%20on%20the%20road%20today%20are%20equipped%20with%20at%20least%20half%20a%20dozen%20sensors%2C%20from%20cameras%20to%20radars%2C%20to%20support%20safety%20features%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwayve-tesla-full-self-driving-comparison-adas-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadvanced%20driver-assistance%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ADAS)%20that%20are%20now%20ubiquitous%20in%20the%20modern%20automotive%20industry.%20And%20as%20automakers%20continue%20to%20offload%20the%20task%20of%20driving%20from%20humans%2C%20cars%20will%20become%20even%20more%20sensorized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKinetic%2C%20a%20Southern%20California-based%20startup%2C%20wants%20to%20scale%20a%20service%20that%20will%20fix%20those%20sensors%20if%20a%20car%20ever%20gets%20into%20a%20collision.%20The%20CEO%20analogizes%20it%20to%20the%20modern%20car's%20optometrist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20eyes%2C%20and%20when%20we%20need%20to%20correct%20vision%2C%20we%20go%20to%20an%20optometrist%20who%20places%20all%20these%20letters%20at%2020%20feet%2C%20measures%20our%20vision%20and%20prescription%2C%20and%20then%20gives%20us%20the%20glasses%20to%20correct%20our%20defect%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20Nikhil%20Naikal%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20same%20way%2C%20this%20is%20a%20digital%20prescription%20to%20correct%20the%20errors%20of%20the%20car's%20understanding%20of%20the%20world%20around%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20car%20is%20the%20same%20as%20it%20once%20was%20after%20its%20first%20fender%20bender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPanels%20get%20bent%2C%20parts%20are%20replaced%2C%20and%20the%20paint%20won't%20match%20the%20original%20exactly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20principle%20goes%20for%20the%20sensors%20on%20a%20car%2C%20Naikal%20said.%20Sensors%20are%20highly%20sensitive%20to%20alignment%2C%20and%20a%20fraction%20of%20a%20degree%20can%20significantly%20affect%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20an%20ADAS%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-fully-self-driving-cars-are-almost-impossible-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eself-driving%20feature%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20vehicle%20is%20in%20a%20front-end%20collision%20or%20rear-ended%2C%20those%20sensors%20could%20be%20thrown%20out%20of%20position.%20Mechanics%20can%20put%20the%20sensors%20back%20in%20place%2C%20but%20they%20won't%20be%20re-mounted%20in%20a%20spot%20perfectly%20identical%20to%20their%20factory%20placement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20where%20Kinetic's%20robotics%20platform%20and%20software%20come%20in%20to%20calibrate%20the%20sensors%20%E2%80%94%20or%2C%20as%20Naikal%20put%20it%2C%20give%20them%20a%20%26quot%3Bdigital%20prescription.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221251b86a-9544-485b-ad37-cb11d1757f28%5C%22%3EThe%20auto%20shop%20of%20the%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAn%208%2C000-square-foot%20facility%20in%20San%20Francisco's%20Dogpatch%20neighborhood%20is%20one%20of%20eight%20Kinetic%20hubs%20on%20the%20West%20Coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20inside%20is%20unlike%20loud%2C%20messy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wrecked-cars-restored-hendricks-auto-body-repair-process-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eauto%20body%20shops%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20Kinetic%20facility%20is%20quiet%20and%20mostly%20empty%20save%20for%20a%20rotating%20platform%20and%20a%20robotic%20arm%20attached%20to%20a%20short%20track.%20A%20typical%20location%20is%20staffed%20with%20up%20to%20two%20technicians%2C%20Naikal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20Wednesday%20afternoon%2C%20Kinetic%20was%20servicing%20a%202022%20Toyota%20Camry%20Hybrid%20LE%20that%20had%20been%20repaired%20at%20a%20local%20body%20shop%20after%20a%20front-end%20collision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20robotic%20arm%20scans%20a%20car.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c741c5f573a637a75671e5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKinetic%20uses%20robotics%20to%20calibrate%20sensors%20on%20a%20car%2C%20post-repair.%3Cp%3ELloyd%20Lee%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20car%20was%20driven%20onto%20the%20platform%2C%20where%20Kinetic's%20camera%20package%20takes%20detailed%20photos%20of%20the%20car%2C%20and%20a%20robotic%20arm%20points%20a%20laser%20at%20the%20radar%20sensor%20embedded%20in%20the%20Toyota's%20grill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKinetic's%20software%20then%20puts%20the%20car%20and%20the%20sensors%20back%20in%20sync.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20car%20thinks%20it's%20going%20to%20do%20and%20what%20the%20sensors%20think%20the%20car%20is%20going%20to%20do%20needs%20to%20be%20aligned%2C%26quot%3B%20Naikal%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20sensor%20thinks%20that%20the%20car%20is%20going%20to%20go%20right%2C%20whereas%20the%20car%20actually%20needs%20to%20go%20left%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20a%20problem.%20It%20causes%20unstable%20things%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fteslas-fsd-car-crash-california-phantom-braking-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eghost%20braking%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20jerking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20process%20takes%20about%2010%20minutes.%20Naikal%20said%20a%20single%20Kinetic%20hub%20can%20service%20about%2080%20cars%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20repair%20shops%20might%20rely%20on%20a%20mobile%20service%2C%20in%20which%20a%20specialized%20technician%20comes%20to%20calibrate%20the%20sensors.%20Naikal%20said%20a%20lot%20of%20body%20shops%20don't%20have%20the%20space%2C%20lighting%2C%20equipment%2C%20or%20trained%20technicians%20that%20can%20accommodate%20an%20in-house%20service.%20Local%20body%20shops%20can%20either%20choose%20to%20send%20cars%20to%20Kinetic's%20hub%20or%2C%20if%20they%20have%20space%2C%20lease%20the%20company's%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202026%2C%20Naikal%20said%20he%20aims%20to%20have%2020%20hubs%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKinetic's%20platform%20can%20also%20perform%20damage%20inspections%20and%20develop%20repair%20plans%2C%20but%20Naikal%20envisions%20servicing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwaymo-robotaxi-depot-san-francisco-what-does-it-look-like-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eautonomous%20vehicle%20fleets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20require%20constant%20cleaning%20and%20sensor%20maintenance%2C%20as%20another%20line%20of%20business.%20The%20future%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20require%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20service%20infrastructure%20built%20around%20robotics%20and%20software%20rather%20than%20a%20traditional%20body%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20more%20than%20just%20Jiffy%20Lubes%20and%20Valvolines%2C%26quot%3B%20Naikal%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20think%20of%20ourselves%20as%20the%20infrastructure%20layer%20for%20the%20future%20of%20autonomy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fself-driving-cars-adas-robotaxi-sensor-repair-kinetic-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774771861000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c7413e8373a547629c74a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fself-driving-cars-adas-robotaxi-sensor-repair-kinetic-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Modern%20cars%20have%20at%20least%20half%20a%20dozen%20sensors%20to%20support%20self-driving%20and%20safety%20features.%20Kinetic%20is%20a%20startup%20that%20specializes%20in%20sensor%20repair.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lloydlee%40insider.com%20(Lloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fself-driving-cars-adas-robotaxi-sensor-repair-kinetic-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'BJP%20says%20can't%20eat%20fish%2C%20meat'%3A%20Mamta%20Banerjee%20campaigns%20in%20Purulia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774771676000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129877264%2Cimgsize-23340.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Felections%2Fassembly-elections%2Fwest-bengal%2Fbjp-says-cant-eat-fish-meat-mamta-banerjee-campaigns-in-purulia%2Farticleshow%2F129877202.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20fiercely%20criticized%20the%20BJP%20in%20Purulia%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20intending%20to%20curb%20local%20food%20habits%20like%20fish%20and%20meat%20consumption.%20She%20also%20alleged%20the%20Election%20Commission's%20voter%20list%20deletions%20targeted%20her%20supporters%20and%20highlighted%20the%20success%20of%20her%20Lakshmir%20Bhandar%20scheme%2C%20warning%20of%20its%20discontinuation%20under%20BJP%20rule.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Oman%20government%20takes%20over%20SalamAir%2C%20airlines%20to%20operate%20separately%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774771286000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-12987