-market-today-nasdaq100-correction-iran-war-tech-stocks-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecorrection%20territory%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20defined%20as%20a%20drawdown%20of%20more%20than%2010%25%20from%20a%20recent%20peak.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20ended%20the%20day%20just%20shy%20of%20a%20correction%20after%20suffering%20five%20straight%20weeks%20of%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reporters%20and%20editors%20scanned%20social%20media%20and%20our%20inboxes%20for%20insights%20from%20top%20financial%20minds%20on%20what's%20driving%20the%20sell-off%20%E2%80%94%20and%20where%20stocks%20may%20be%20headed%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20responses%20largely%20pointed%20in%20the%20same%20direction%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-today-and-oil-prices-spike-trump-iran-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20White%20House%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20from%20Barclays%20put%20it%20this%20way%3A%20%26quot%3BFlip-flopping%20and%20headline%20fatigue%20is%20starting%20to%20seriously%20undermine%20the%20efficacy%20of%20the%20'Trump%20put'%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20a%20popular%20options%20trade%20that%20protects%20against%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20refers%20to%20a%20popular%20belief%20that%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20will%20step%20in%20to%20support%20markets%20during%20downturns.%20Increasingly%2C%20investors%20are%20losing%20faith%20in%20that%20backstop%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20end%20of%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20smart%20people%20are%20saying%20about%20the%20latest%20market%20sell-off%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22875de35e-8f0c-4571-a827-d8cb73248622%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMohamed%20A.%20El-Erian%2C%20economist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFamed%20economist%20and%20former%20PIMCO%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-economic-impact-oil-prices-inflation-supply-el-erian-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMohamed%20A.%20El-Erian%3C%2Fa%3E%20wrote%20on%20X%20that%20markets%20ended%20the%20week%20on%20a%20volatile%20note%2C%20with%20both%20stocks%20and%20bonds%20falling.%20He%20pointed%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-strategy-60-40-portfolio-recession-us-economy-jim-paulsen-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3B60%2F40%26quot%3B%20portfolio%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%2060%25%20stocks%20and%2040%25%20bonds%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20sign%20that%20even%20diversified%20investors%20are%20taking%20a%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20typical%20market%20environment%2C%20bonds%20help%20cushion%20the%20losses%20when%20stocks%20decline.%20But%20amid%20this%20week's%20sell-off%2C%20even%20balanced%20portfolios%20are%20under%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20rough%20end%20to%20the%20trading%20week%20for%20both%20US%20stocks%20and%20bonds%2C%20worsening%20a%20month%20where%20the%20classic%20'diversified'%2060%2F40%20portfolio%20is%20experiencing%20its%20steepest%20monthly%20loss%20since%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20El-Erian%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22153c88b7-230e-4c07-af1c-edd555d658db%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarko%20Kolanovic%2C%20former%20JPMorgan%20chief%20market%20strategist%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMarko%20Kolanovic%2C%20former%20JPMorgan%20chief%20market%20strategist%2C%20wrote%20in%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Friday%20that%20delaying%20the%20reopening%20of%20the%20Hormuz%20Strait%20%E2%80%94%20a%20critical%20waterway%20for%20the%20world's%20energy%20supply%20%E2%80%94%20is%20harming%20the%20global%20economy%2C%20and%20that%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20tactics%20to%20calm%20oil%20prices%20have%20not%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20verbal%20gymnastic%20from%20the%20administration%20to%20keep%20oil%20prices%20low%20was%20in%20the%20end%20counterproductive.%20Masking%20the%20magnitude%20of%20the%20problem%20and%20delaying%20actions%20to%20reopen%20Hormuz.%20Buying%20time%20%E2%80%94%20but%20time%20that%20works%20against%20the%20global%20economy%20so%20effectively%20in%20favor%20of%20Iran%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c92b45a3-5594-4b37-8037-3e985b7a7cbe%5C%22%3EPeter%20Mallouk%2C%20CEO%20of%20Creative%20Planning%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeter%20Mallouk%2C%20CEO%20and%20president%20of%20Creative%20Planning%2C%20a%20wealth%20management%20firm%2C%20framed%20the%20sell-off%20as%20driven%20by%20short-term%20noise%20in%20a%20Friday%20post%20on%20X%2C%20adding%20that%20only%20one%20thing%20matters%20in%20the%20long%20run%3A%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20matters%20in%20the%20short%20run%3A%20wars%2C%20oil%20prices%2C%20tariffs%2C%20interest%20rates%2C%20sentiment%2C%20a%20million%20other%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20What%20matters%20in%20the%20long%20run%3A%20Earnings.%20Speculators%20focus%20on%20the%20short%20run.%20Investors%20play%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-speeding-up-fundamental-investing-jpmorgan-alliance-bernstein-blackrock-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong%20game%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229ab660bb-47a1-4fa4-851b-2fe8aafd20ef%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETorsten%20Sl%C3%B8k%2C%20chief%20economist%20of%20Apollo%20Global%20Management%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETorsten%20Sl%C3%B8k%20also%20took%20the%20contrarian%20view%20that%20the%20Iran%20war%20won't%20have%20long-term%20impacts%20on%20the%20broader%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMarkets%20are%20overreacting%20to%20what%20will%20likely%20be%20a%204-%20to%206-week%20period%20of%20volatility%2C%20which%20will%20ultimately%20result%20in%2050%20years%20of%20stability%20in%20oil%20markets%2C%20supply%20chains%20and%20geopolitics%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-economy-outlook-iran-war-market-overreaction-oil-prices-apollo-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etop%20Apollo%20economist%3C%2Fa%3E%20added%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BGulf%20region%20will%20become%20more%20stable%20and%20even%20more%20closely%20integrated%20with%20the%20global%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b744f58a-6277-446e-b542-82e26489a500%5C%22%3EPeter%20Tuchman%2C%20'Einstein%20of%20Wall%20Street'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeter%20Tuchman%2C%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20trader%20better%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BEinstein%20of%20Wall%20Street%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20on%20X%20that%20March%20is%20on%20pace%20to%20be%20the%20worst%20month%20since%202022%20and%20warns%20of%20major%20inflationary%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20end%20in%20sight%20with%20this%20war.%20Oil%20is%20going%20up%2C%20up%2C%20up.%20When%20you've%20got%20oil%20at%20the%20levels%20where%20it's%20at%20for%20a%20sustained%20period%20of%20time%2C%20the%20inflationary%20impact%20is%20huge%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20the%20problem%20lies%2C%26quot%3B%20Tuchman%20said%20in%20a%20video%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20adding%20that%20interest%20rates%20may%20rise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263f57c79-6930-4db0-be62-6c6f74457657%5C%22%3ELarry%20Weiss%2C%20head%20of%20trading%20at%20Instinet%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELarry%20Weiss%2C%20Instinet's%20head%20of%20trading%2C%20said%20investors%20are%20skeptical%20of%20reassurances%20from%20administration%20officials%20about%20the%20war's%20timeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeiss%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20market%20would%20have%20popped%26quot%3B%20after%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20said%20the%20war%20would%20take%20%26quot%3Bweeks%2C%20not%20months%26quot%3B%20to%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%26quot%3Bno%20one%20knows%20the%20next%20steps%2C%20and%20there's%20an%20inherent%20distrust%20regarding%20the%20statements%20made%20by%20both%20the%20administration%20and%20the%20Iranians%2C%26quot%3B%20Bloomberg%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2289bcab56-9513-4011-a9a1-ae1b6e88ceaa%5C%22%3EMark%20Zandi%2C%20chief%20economist%20of%20Moody's%20Analytics%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-economy-recession-outlook-gdp-iran-mark-zandi-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMark%20Zandi%20of%20Moody's%20Analytics%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20price%20of%20oil%20needs%20to%20near%20%24125%20per%20barrel%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20the%20year%20for%20the%20US%20economy%20to%20reach%20a%20tipping%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20simulations%20of%20our%20global%20macroeconomic%20model%2C%20oil%20prices%20would%20only%20need%20to%20average%20close%20to%20%24125%20per%20barrel%20in%20the%20second%20quarter%20of%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Zandi%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BWith%20tensions%20still%20elevated%2C%20that's%20not%20a%20stretch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20barrel%20of%20Brent%20crude%20was%20hovering%20around%20%24112%20as%20of%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263f9d0f4-5848-4d44-8cfd-a4034208577d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBarclays%20European%20Equity%20Strategy%20analysts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-stocks-oil-price-iran-markets-war-wall-street-sell-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrump's%20de-escalation%3C%2Fa%3E%20talk%20has%20kept%20equities%20afloat.%20But%20constant%20flip-flopping%20and%20headline%20fatigue%20is%20starting%20to%20undermine%20the%20put%20efficacy%2C%26quot%3B%20Barclays%20European%20Equity%20Strategy%20analysts%20wrote%20in%20a%20Friday%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20war%20goes%20on%2C%20the%20stagflation%20threat%20grows%2C%20though%20the%20energy%20shock%20for%20Europe%20is%20not%20as%20severe%20as%20in%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20Russia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2278d3771c-b93b-4649-b917-9db5190ef621%5C%22%3EJPMorgan%20analysts%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20at%20JPMorgan%20project%20a%20slowdown%20in%20global%20growth%20and%20a%201-percentage-point%20increase%20in%20inflation%2C%20even%20if%20tensions%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20ease%20later%20in%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bbaseline%26quot%3B%20scenario%20is%20that%20the%20price%20of%20Brent%20crude%20remains%20elevated%20through%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20year%2C%20the%20analysts%20wrote%20on%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BIf%20followed%20by%20a%20receding%20of%20tensions%20that%20push%20oil%20to%20%2480bbl%20(%2480%20a%20barrel%20of%20oil)%2C%20we%20estimate%202026%20global%20growth%20will%20be%20lowered%20by%200.6%25%20and%20CPI%20inflation%20raised%20by%201%25.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20scenario%20in%20which%20the%20Strait%20remains%20closed%20for%20another%20month%20could%20push%20crude%20oil%20prices%20to%20%24150%20per%20barrel%2C%20the%20analysts%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarket-sell-off-iran-war-analysis-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774749525000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c85c11f573a637a7567330%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fmarket-sell-off-iran-war-analysis-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Stocks%20plunged%20amid%20the%20US-Iran%20conflict%2C%20with%20Dow%20and%20Nasdaq%20in%20correction%2C%20even%20as%20administration%20officials%20attempt%20to%20quell%20investor%20concerns.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kwhitehouse%40insider.com%20(Kaja%20Whitehouse%2CTristan%20Anthony%2CLloyd%20Lee)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fmarket-sell-off-iran-war-analysis-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Expert%20to%20Anthropic%20supporters%3A%20Judge%20order%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20co%E2