3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deal%2C%20which%20requires%20sign-off%20from%20a%20judge%2C%20would%20pay%20%26quot%3Ball%20women%20who%20were%20sexually%20abused%20or%20trafficked%20by%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%2C%20or%20by%20any%20person%20who%20is%20connected%20to%20or%20otherwise%20associated%20with%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20or%20any%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20sex-trafficking%20venture%2C%20between%20June%2030%2C%202008%20and%20July%206%2C%202019%2C%20inclusive%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.nysd.651138%2Fgov.uscourts.nysd.651138.122.0.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20filing%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawyers%20have%20said%20they%20are%20aware%20of%20%26quot%3Bat%20least%2060%20women%20who%20were%20victimized%20by%20Epstein%26quot%3B%20during%20that%20time%20period%2C%20the%20filing%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20District%20Judge%20Jed%20Rakoff%2C%20who%20is%20overseeing%20the%20case%2C%20gave%20the%20parties%20a%20March%2027%20deadline%20to%20file%20the%20terms%20of%20settlement%20and%20an%20April%202%20hearing%20to%20decide%20whether%20to%20approve%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-victim-lawsuit-bank-of-america-settlement-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBank%20of%20America%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20deal%20allows%20it%20to%20%26quot%3Bput%20this%20matter%20behind%20us%20and%20provides%20further%20closure%20for%20the%20plaintiffs.%26quot%3B%20The%20bank%20continues%20to%20deny%20wrongdoing%3A%20%26quot%3BBank%20of%20America%20did%20not%20facilitate%20sex%20trafficking%20crimes%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEpstein%2C%20known%20for%20rubbing%20elbows%20with%20titans%20of%20industry%20and%20political%20powerhouses%2C%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fepstein-files-show-fbi-probed-4chan-posts-prison-death-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5