l%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftable-space-leases-1-45-lakh-sq-feet-commercial-space-in-gurugram-126032800791_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftable-space-leases-1-45-lakh-sq-feet-commercial-space-in-gurugram-126032800791_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftable-space-leases-1-45-lakh-sq-feet-commercial-space-in-gurugram-126032800791_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22And%20then%20there%20were%20none%3A%20Musk's%20last%20xAI%20cofounder%20is%20out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20with%20his%20hand%20on%20his%20head%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c7d469f573a637a75672a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20has%20said%20xAI%20is%20being%20%26quot%3Brebuilt%20from%20the%20foundations%20up.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EAdrees%20Latif%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElon%20Musk%20started%20xAI%20with%2011%20cofounders%20in%202023.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20last%20remaining%20one%2C%20Ross%20Nordeen%2C%20has%20now%20exited%20the%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMusk%20recently%20said%20xAI%20was%20not%20built%20right%20and%20that%20he's%20reorganizing%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20original%20team%20of%20xAI%20cofounders%20has%20cleared%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20Nordeen%2C%20one%20of%20the%2011%20who%20helped%20build%20the%20company%20alongside%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20left%20the%20company%20this%20week%2C%20according%20to%20people%20with%20knowledge%20of%20his%20departure.%20Nordeen%20has%20also%20lost%20the%20badge%20on%20X%20that%20identifies%20him%20as%20an%20xAI%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20exit%20comes%20as%20Musk%20reorganizes%20xAI%20and%20preps%20for%20a%20blockbuster%20initial%20public%20offering%20of%20his%20rocket%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-sends-staff-q-and-a-on-spacex-merger-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpaceX%2C%20which%20acquired%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20startup%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2036-year-old%20Nordeen%20reported%20directly%20to%20Musk%20at%20xAI%20and%20served%20as%20his%20right-hand%20operator%2C%20coordinating%20priorities%20and%20driving%20execution%20across%20the%20company%2C%20insiders%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENordeen%2C%20a%20Michigan%20Tech%20grad%2C%20followed%20Musk%20from%20Tesla%20to%20cofound%20the%20AI%20startup%20in%202023.%20At%20Tesla%2C%20Nordeen%20was%20a%20technical%20program%20manager%20on%20the%20Autopilot%20team%20and%20worked%20on%20building%20out%20data%20centers%20to%20train%20Tesla's%20Full%20Self-Driving%20system%2C%20according%20to%20a%202021%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-salary-database-elon-musk-pay-strategy-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganizational%20chart%20%3C%2Fa%3Eviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENordeen%20is%20a%20longtime%20friend%20of%20Musk's%20cousin%2C%20James%20Musk%2C%20according%20to%20Walter%20Isaacson's%20biography%20of%20the%20billionaire.%20Nordeen%20was%20also%20one%20of%20a%20few%20dozen%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%20engineers%20who%20helped%20Musk%20coordinate%20large-scale%20cuts%20at%20Twitter%20after%20he%20took%20over%20the%20company%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXAI%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%20Nordeen%20did%20not%20return%20calls%20or%20an%20email%20from%20Business%20Insider%2C%20though%20he%20did%20post%20a%20photo%20on%20X%20on%20Saturday%20suggesting%20he's%20getting%20some%20rest%20and%20relaxation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXAI%20has%20lost%20eight%20cofounders%20since%20January%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmanuel-kroiss-xai-cofounder-departure-elon-musk-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EManuel%20Kroiss%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-cofounders-guodong-zhang-zihang-dai-depart-elon-musk-company-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGuodong%20Zhang%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Zihang%20Dai%2C%20Toby%20Pohlen%2C%20Jimmy%20Ba%2C%20Tony%20Wu%2C%20and%20Greg%20Yang.%20Kroiss%2C%20who%20led%20pretraining%2C%20which%20helps%20train%20the%20company's%20AI%20models%20on%20large%20datasets%20and%20reported%20directly%20to%20Musk%2C%20left%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20departures%20began%20shortly%20after%20SpaceX's%20merger%20with%20xAI%20ahead%20of%20the%20IPO%20that%20could%20be%20the%20most%20valuable%20in%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Musk%20reorganized%20xAI%20and%20unveiled%20a%20new%20structure.%20Since%20then%2C%20many%20of%20the%20leaders%20Musk%20put%20in%20charge%20of%20key%20projects%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20company's%20coding%20tool%20to%20image%20generation%20%E2%80%94%20have%20left%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXAI%20has%20gone%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-leadership-style-big-year-grok-ipo-spacex-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseveral%20restructurings%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20and%20has%20been%20in%20flux%2C%20shedding%20dozens%20of%20employees%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20last%20few%20months%20after%20the%20company%20cut%20portions%20of%20its%20teams%20working%20on%20its%20video%20and%20image%20generation%20tool%2C%20Grok%20Imagine%2C%20and%20Macrohard%2C%20its%20AI%20agent%20project%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best-funded%20players%20in%20the%20AI%20race%20and%20has%20reached%20a%20reported%20valuation%20of%20around%20%24250%20billion%2C%20but%20it%20trails%20behind%20major%20players%20like%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20scale%20and%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20%26quot%3BxAI%20was%20not%20built%20right%20first%20time%20around%2C%20so%20is%20being%20rebuilt%20from%20the%20foundations%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20said%20the%20company%20is%20actively%20recruiting%20new%20talent%20and%20looking%20at%20candidates%20who%20were%20previously%20passed%20over.%20The%20company%20has%20brought%20on%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20recruits%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%2C%20including%20two%20senior%20leaders%20from%20AI%20coding%20company%20Cursor%2C%20Andrew%20Milich%20and%20Jason%20Ginsberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20xAI%20or%20have%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Agkay%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Egkay%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20248-894-6012.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20device%2C%20and%20nonwork%20WiFi%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-cofounder-ross-nordeen-leaves-musk-preps-spacex-ipo-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774710233000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c7e1e5f573a637a75672af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-cofounder-ross-nordeen-leaves-musk-preps-spacex-ipo-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20is%20shaking%20up%20xAI%20ahead%20of%20the%20SpaceX%20IPO.%20All%2011%20of%20his%20cofounders%20are%20gone%2C%20