22I%20dreaded%20being%20asked%20what%20I%20did%20for%20fun.%20As%20a%20working%20mom%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20an%20answer.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20painting%20canvas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69baf89dd387710cb9e45f97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20started%20painting%20again.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20used%20to%20dread%20being%20asked%20what%20I%20did%20for%20fun%20as%20a%20working%20mom.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20started%20carving%20out%20small%2C%20creative%20moments%20in%20my%20daily%20life.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThose%20habits%20helped%20me%20feel%20more%20like%20myself%20and%20less%20depleted.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20the%20question%20at%20the%20office%20every%20Monday%2C%20as%20I%20got%20coffee%2C%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20did%20you%20do%20for%20fun%20over%20the%20weekend%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20question%20made%20me%20want%20to%20crawl%20under%20the%20table.%20Not%20because%20I%20didn't%20love%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskip-small-talk-have-deep-conversations-2016-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esmall%20talk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20because%20as%20a%20young%20executive%20juggling%20a%20demanding%20job%2C%20two%20little%20kids%2C%20and%20the%20constant%20low-grade%20scramble%20of%20just%20getting%20through%20the%20day%2C%20contemplating%20this%20question%20after%20a%20long%20parenting%20weekend%20felt%20like%20a%20cruel%20joke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20typically%20responded%20back%20with%20something%20lame%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20really%20nice%2C%20thanks%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20quickly%20turned%20the%20question%20back%20to%20them%2C%20which%20would%20be%201000%25%20more%20interesting.%20Especially%20because%20I%20worked%20with%20talented%20designers%2C%20researchers%2C%20strategists%2C%20and%20futurists.%20Over%20the%20weekend%2C%20they%20definitely%20learned%20how%20to%20DJ%2C%20planned%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-honeymooned-in-costa-rica-during-the-off-season-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrip%20to%20Costa%20Rica%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20painted%20a%20mural%20for%20a%20local%20coffee%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20honest%20answer%2C%20never%20spoken%20out%20loud%2C%20would%20have%20been%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20watched%20my%20kids%20grind%20Play-Doh%20into%20the%20carpet%2C%20get%20into%2010%20fights%2C%20and%20devour%20all%20my%20berries.%20It%20was%20riveting.%26quot%3B%20Not%20exactly%20the%20best%20commentary%20for%20an%20early-morning%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fholiday-party-ice-breaker-questions-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoffice%20icebreaker%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I'm%20being%20honest%20with%20myself%2C%20I%20was%20jealous.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-shaming-partying-community-connect-fun-mamas-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emissed%20having%20a%20fun%3C%2Fa%3E%20response%20to%20the%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2284fb01d2-00ca-4ae9-b0cd-4c6b894989c3%5C%22%3EI%20had%20artistic%20dreams%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20always%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbeing-too-creative-could-harm-your-career-according-to-scientist-2019-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreative%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ever%20since%20I%20was%20a%20kid%20with%20an%20artistic%20dream%2C%20glitter%2C%20and%20a%20glue%20gun.%20I%20would%20spend%20hours%20coming%20up%20with%20crafts%2C%20ride%20my%20bike%20to%20get%20supplies%2C%20design%20them%20with%20my%20friends%20for%20days%2C%20and%20eventually%20sell%20them%20on%20the%20sidewalk%20in%20my%20neighborhood.%20That%20creative%20spirit%20continued%20into%20my%20pre-parent%20life%3A%20painting%2C%20DIY%20home%20repairs%2C%20jewelry%20making%2C%20and%20throwing%20dinner%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20I'm%20in%20the%20self-proclaimed%20%26quot%3Bmiddle%20motherhood%26quot%3B%20stage%20of%20parenting%20with%20more%20independent%20elementary-%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting-teens-is-a-balance-too-close-or-too-far-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emiddle%20school-aged%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20have%20a%20bit%20more%20time%20on%20my%20hands.%20In%20this%20new%20stage%20of%20parenting%2C%20I%20want%20to%20be%20able%20to%20answer%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20you%20do%20for%20fun%3F%26quot%3B%20with%20something%20unique%20and%20creative%2C%20honoring%20the%20little%20girl%20with%20paint-splattered%20overalls%20and%20big%20artistic%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221abbf558-8276-4341-8ec2-176c7ef22edd%5C%22%3EI%20started%20painting%20again%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20started%20this%20quest%20to%20infuse%20more%20creativity%20into%20my%20life.%20Starting%20out%20small%2C%20I%20pulled%20out%20paintbrushes%20I%20hadn't%20touched%20in%20a%20decade%20and%20found%20an%20easel%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-i-furnished-my-apartment-for-under-1100-thanks-to-facebook-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFacebook%20Marketplace%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20set%20up%20in%20my%20office%20area%2C%20and%20my%20background%20became%20my%20painting%20progress.%20Being%20a%20mom%20and%20an%20executive%2C%20I%20couldn't%20paint%20for%20hours%20at%20once.%20Instead%2C%20my%20painting%20sessions%20were%2030%20seconds%20between%20bathtime%20or%2015%20minutes%20during%20a%20lunch%20break.%20When%20I%20had%20a%20moment%2C%20I%20would%20take%20a%20couple%20of%20swipes%20with%20acrylic%20paint.%20Over%20time%2C%20the%20painting%20started%20to%20reveal%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221454%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20on%20computer%20camera%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bafc6debc245a53a8119a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221178%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20I%20was%20nervous%20about%20sharing%20my%20background%20art%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzoom-masturbation-men-exposing-themselves-private-zoombombing-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EZoom%20meetings%3C%2Fa%3E.%20What%20would%20my%20talented%20designer%20colleagues%20say%20about%20my%20mediocre%2C%20mom-ish%2C%20abstract%20artwork%3F%20But%20guess%20what%3A%20they%20loved%20it!%20It%20became%20a%20positive%20topic%20of%20conversation%20on%20calls.%20They%20would%20catch%20new%20strokes%2C%20comment%20on%20techniques%20I%20used%2C%20or%20provide%20advice%20when%20I%20was%20stuck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20something%2C%20even%20badly%2C%20felt%20like%20hitting%20a%20reset%20button%20in%20my%20brain.%20I%20felt%20more%20alive%20and%20calm%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20So%20I%20kept%20going%2C%20aiming%20for%20bite-sized%20creative%20bursts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225a5914d5-ef6e-41ad-b38e-67ec60753f8f%5C%22%3EI%20kept%20doing%20creative%20little%20things%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20took%20my%20creativity%20on%20the%20road%2C%20packing%20friendship%20bracelet%20supplies%20for%20my%20son's%20travel%20baseball%20tournaments%20so%20my%20daughter%20and%20I%20could%20pass%20the%20time.%20Every%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20another%20feral%20sports%20sibling%20would%20join%2C%20and%20I%20played%20camp%20counselor%2C%20showcasing%20my%20superior%20bracelet-making%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20girls'%20trip%2C%20I%20brought%20paint%20gems%20%E2%80%94%20just%20like%20paint-by-numbers%2C%20but%20with%20sticky%20paper%20designs%20like%20plants%20and%20tiny%20plastic%20bits%20that%20stick%20to%20the%20paper.%20It's%20an%20absolute%20joy%2C%20especially%20the%20ASMR%20effect%20of%20all%20those%20plastic%20pieces%20clicking%20into%20place.%20And%20afterward%20it%20became%20a%20family%20activity%2C%20our%20dining%20room%20table%20littered%20with%20gems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmboldened%20by%20these%20small%20creative%20steps%2C%20I%20took%20a%20leap%20to%20start%20writing%20again.%20I%20wrote%20to%20process%20my%20feelings%20about%20parenting%2C%20share%20my%20leadership%20experiences%2C%20and%20put%20my%20UW-Madison%20Journalism%20degree%20to%20good%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Paintings%20in%20office%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bb0091d387710cb9e45fe4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPainting%20made%20the%20author%20more%20patient.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20creative%20action%20was%20taking%20me%20to%20new%20heights%2C%20and%20I%20hadn't%20realized%20how%20much%20I%20needed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227fdd0a15-13c6-4609-ab48-561dc85a4fa5%5C%22%3EBeing%20creative%20helps%20me%20in%20ways%20I%20hadn't%20thought%20of%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20learned%20that%20when%20I%20give%20myself%20even%20tiny%20pockets%20of%20creative%20time%2C%20I'm%20more%20patient.%20I%20don't%20feel%20as%20depleted.%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20making%20something%2C%20even%20if%20it%20takes%20time%20and%20isn't%20outcome-driven%2C%20quietly%20brings%20me%20back%20to%20myself%20and%20makes%20me%20an%20even%20more%20present%20parent.%20In%20my%20opinion%2C%20parents%20should%20be%20doing%20it%20more%2C%20not%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20long%20time%2C%20I%20treated%20creativity%20like%20a%20luxury%2C%20even%20though%20it%20was%20part%20of%20my%20day%20job%20running%20a%20design%20and%20innovation%20studio.%20Sure%2C%20I%20could%20do%20it%20for%20clients%20and%20colleagues.%20But%20for%20%3Cem%3Emyself%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20treated%20it%20like%20something%20I'd%20return%20to%20when%20life%20slowed%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20is%2C%20parenthood%20doesn't%20really%20work%20that%20way.%20It%20never%20slows%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-mom-creativity-habits-find-yourself-again-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774709221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bafff275bee4e0ee55dc42%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-mom-creativity-habits-find-yourself-again-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20a%20busy%20working%20mom%2C%20I%20dreaded%20being%20asked%20what%20I%20did%20for%20fun.%20Small%20creative%20habits%20helped%20me%20feel%20more%20like%20myself%20again.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Schlott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-mom-creativity-habits-find-yourself-again-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Expectant%20mothers%20in%20Cuba%20struggle%20under%20fuel%20blockade%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774707286000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F38cb%2Flive%2Fe5c2e140-29f0-11f1-934f-036468834728.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc8dl9n7gvdgo%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BBC's%20Will%20Grant%20speaks%20to%20two%20women%20experiencing%20starkly%20different%20realities%20as%20the%20country's%20energy%20crisis%20impacts%20their%20pregnancies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc8dl9n7gvdgo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Where%20to%20Watch%20Moses%20Itauma%20vs.%20Jermaine%20Franklin%20Boxing%20Live%20Online%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published