%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20while%20the%20NGO%20partners%20on%20the%20ground%20will%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F287345%2Fseeds-disaster-cyclone-earthquake-india-how-to-build-safe-homes-schools%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistributing%20the%20relief%20kits%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20funds%20will%20be%20directly%20channelled%20towards%20procuring%20the%20necessary%20material%20and%20will%20not%20be%20directed%20to%20NGOs%20themselves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYour%20money%20is%20directly%20helping%20a%20flood%20victim.%20Your%20donations%20will%20go%20towards%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20airlifting%20the%20boats%20to%20the%20sites%20of%20rescue%20operations%20and%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20procuring%20relief%20material%20so%20that%20families%20can%20be%20helped%20once%20they%20are%20shifted%20to%20the%20relief%20centres.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FDisaster-Relief%2FThe-Better-India%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Clabel%3EDONATE%20NOW%20%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20943px)%20100vw%2C%20943px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22943%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20relief%20requirements%20by%20the%20people%20who%20are%20being%20sheltered%20at%20camps%20after%20being%20rescued%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937.png%20943w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937-300x219.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937-500x365.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937-768x560.png%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FScreenshot-2025-09-05-173515-1757073937-150x109.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496953%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22688%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20relief%20requirements%20of%20the%20people%20who%20are%20being%20sheltered%20at%20camps%20after%20being%20rescued%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESchools%20%26amp%3B%20gurudwaras%20turn%20into%20relief%20camps%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20necessity%20of%20boats%20during%20this%20time%2C%20Harmeet%20shares%20that%20these%20are%20of%20paramount%20importance%20in%20the%20Fazilka%20area%20of%20Punjab.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20where%20the%20rivers%20meet%2C%20and%20so%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20flood%20is%20a%20lot.%20The%20water%20has%20increased%20to%20a%20high%20level%20here.%E2%80%9D%20Boats%20are%20the%20only%20form%20of%20conveyance%20right%20now%20across%20the%20districts%20of%20Punjab%3A%20Gurdaspur%2C%20Pathankot%2C%20Ferozepur%2C%20Amritsar%2C%20and%20Fazilka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAcross%20Punjab%2C%20gurudwaras%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20other%20public%20institutions%20have%20been%20turned%20into%20relief%20camps.%20The%20Kalgidhar%20Trust%20runs%20100%2B%20schools%2C%20and%20these%20too%20have%20been%20transformed%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F432303%2Fnon-profit-organisations-helping-conflict-affected-communities-india-manipur-kashmir-pahalgam-attack%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecentres%20where%20people%20are%20being%20sheltered%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20the%20situation%20eases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5C